Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玄黄端现 太极混沌如鸡蛋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In the beginning, there was darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.12,0:00:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着轰的一声\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then, bang...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诞生了无限膨胀的时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}giving birth to an endless expanding existence...of time, space, and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.05,0:00:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在所见超乎我们的想象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, see further than we've ever imagined...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.34,0:00:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越了客观认知极限\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}beyond the limits of our existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方我们称之为"宇宙"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a place we call "The Universe."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这或许是行星科学的圣杯\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's perhaps the holy grail of planetary science.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是宇宙中独一无二的吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Are we alone in the universe?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.69,0:00:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们要回答的最重大的问题之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's one of the grandest questions we could answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.07,0:00:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们其实并没有生命的定义\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We don't really have a definition of life...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我认为发现之时就会知道了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but l think l'll know it when l discover it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命可能会迂回曲折\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Life can take many twists and turns...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.62,0:00:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为它最酷的地方\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and l think the really cool thing about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我们有可能在别处看到的种类\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is the variety that we're going to be able to find else where.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是一颗孤独的行星 抑或地球以外还有生命存在？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Are we a lonely planet, or does life exist beyond Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.55,0:01:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天体生物学前沿领域的同仁们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Members of the groundbreaking field of astrobiology...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经联合起来共同解决这个未解之谜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}havejoined forces to solve this enduring mystery.
